name: Top 200 Worldwide
content:
##This data set is no longer being supported and will be removed from App Lab on December 1, 2021##

Description: top 200 songs worldwide on spotify, data is updated everyday

Source: [Spotify](https://spotifycharts.com/regional/)

Processing: downloaded .csv from spotify

Columns:

* Track Name (string): name of the song
* Artist (string): name of the artist of the song
* Position (numerical): ranking number of the song
* Streams (numerical): number of times the song has been streamed
* URL (string): link to the song on spotify
